## Completeness Checklist
- [ ] User story written in standard As a/I want/So that format
- [ ] At least 3 BDD scenarios written (happy path, edge case, failure case)
- [ ] AI-specific criteria defined where story involves AI/ML
- [ ] Non-functional acceptance criteria specified
- [ ] Definition of Done reference linked
- [ ] Criteria reviewed and accepted by Product Owner
